"      Approach to the patient with colonic polyps",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/2/11304?source=see_link\">",
"      Bleeding after colonic polypectomy",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/39/17016?source=see_link\">",
"      Clinical manifestations and diagnosis of familial adenomatous polyposis",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/59/19386?source=see_link\">",
"      Clinical features and diagnosis of Lynch syndrome (hereditary nonpolyposis colorectal cancer)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?41/25/42394?source=see_link\">",
"      Colorectal cancer: Epidemiology, risk factors, and protective factors",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
